quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Ta ha
  20,2,Humne yeh Quran tumpar is liye nazil nahin kiya hai ke tum museebat mein padh jao
  20,3,Yeh to ek yaad dihani hai har us shaks ke liye jo darey
  20,4,Nazil kiya gaya hai us zaat ki taraf se jisne paida kiya hai zameen ko aur buland aasmano ko
  20,5,Woh Rehman (qayanaat ke) takht e sultanat par jalwa farma hai
  20,6,Maalik hai un sab cheezon ka jo aasmano aur zameen mein hain aur jo zameen o aasmaan ke darmiyan mein hain aur jo mitti ke nichey hain
  20,7,"Tum chahe apni baat pukar kar kaho, woh to chupke se kahi hui baat balke issey makhfi-tar (most secret) baat bhi jaanta hai"
  20,8,"Woh Allah hai, uske siwa koi khuda nahin, uske liye behtareen naam hain"
  20,9,Aur tumhein kuch Moosa ki khabar bhi pahunchi hai
  20,10,"Jabke usne ek aag dekhi aur apne ghar walon se kaha ke “ zara thehro, maine ek aag dekhi hai, shayad ke tumhare liye ek-aad angara le aaon, ya is aag par mujhey (raaste ke mutaalik) koi rehnumayi (guidance) mil jaye”"
  20,11,Wahan pahuncha to pukara gaya “Aey Moosa
  20,12,"Main hi tera Rubb hoon, jutiyan (shoes) utaar de, tu waadi e muqaddas Tuwa mein hai"
  20,13,"Aur maine tujhko chun liya hai, sun jo kuch wahee kiya jata hai"
  20,14,"Main hi Allah hoon, mere siwa koi khuda nahin hai, pas tu meri bandagi kar aur meri yaad ke liye namaz qayam kar"
  20,15,"Qayamat ki ghadi zaroor aane wali hai, main uska waqt makhfi rakhna chahta hoon, taa-ke har mutanaffis apni saii(labours/koshish) ke mutabik badla paye"
  20,16,"Pas koi aisa shaks jo uspar iman nahin laata aur apni khwahish e nafs ka banda ban gaya hai tujhko us ghadi ki fikr se na roak de, warna tu halakat mein padh jayega"
  20,17,"Aur aey Moosa, yeh tere haath mein kya hai?”"
  20,18,"Moosa ne jawab diya “yeh meri laathi hai, ispar taik laga kar chalta hoon, issey apni bakriyon ke liye pattey jhadta hoon, aur bhi bahut se kaam hain jo issey leta hoon”"
  20,19,Farmaya “phenk de isko Moosa”
  20,20,Usne phenk diya aur yakayak woh ek saanp (snake) thi jo daud raha tha
  20,21,"Farmaya “pakad le isko aur darr nahin, hum isey phir waisa hi kardenge jaisi yeh thi"
  20,22,"Aur zara apna haath apni bagal mein daba, chamakta hua niklega bagair kisi takleef ke, yeh dusri nishani hai"
  20,23,Is liye ke hum tujhey apni badi nishniyan dikane waley hain
  20,24,"Ab tu Firoun ke paas jaa, woh sarkash ho gaya hai”"